    {
      "id": "9bdc5a62-cbf6-4df7-b8e1-3f0b844506a2",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $0 < a_1 < a_2 < \\dots < a_p$ des réels fixés.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(0 &lt; a_1 &lt; a_2 &lt; \\dots &lt; a_p\\)</span> des réels fixés.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3b70e1df-16e3-42ed-ac7b-d35a873959df",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que pour tout réel $a > a_p$ il existe un unique réel $x_a > 0$\n      solution de l'équation : $a_1^x + \\dots + a_p^x = a^x$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que pour tout réel <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a &gt; a_p\\)</span> il existe un unique réel <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_a &gt; 0\\)</span> solution de l’équation : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_1^x + \\dots + a_p^x = a^x\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6b360854-f720-43b7-a515-bc4f70e08e8d",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "\\'Etude de $x \\mapsto \\left(\\frac{a_1}a\\right)^x + \\dots + \\left(\\frac{a_p}a\\right)^x$.",
        "html": "<p>Étude de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x \\mapsto \\left(\\frac{a_1}a\\right)^x + \\dots + \\left(\\frac{a_p}a\\right)^x\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b88bd63a-ac77-4ee4-a2ea-6be0ac8b62d8",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Pour $a < b$, comparer $x_a$ et $x_b$.",
        "html": "<p>Pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a &lt; b\\)</span>, comparer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_a\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_b\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7e770-89d3-4d90-bfc6-d57adba5c4d7",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$x_a > x_b$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_a &gt; x_b\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d42e3940-07f1-4db4-927e-b7058d80da03",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Chercher $\\lim_{a\\to+\\infty} x_a$ puis\n      $\\lim_{a\\to+\\infty} x_a\\ln a$",
        "html": "<p>Chercher <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim_{a\\to+\\infty} x_a\\)</span> puis <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim_{a\\to+\\infty} x_a\\ln a\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c496ee7e-82a3-4289-996b-dc4806c38c30",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$x_a\\to\\ell$.\n               Si $\\ell > 0$, $a^{a_a} \\to +\\infty$, mais\n               $a_1^{x_a} + \\dots + a_p^{x_a} \\to a_1^\\ell + \\dots + a_p^\\ell$.\n\n               Donc $\\ell = 0$, et $x_a\\ln a \\to \\ln p$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_a\\to\\ell\\)</span>. Si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\ell &gt; 0\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a^{a_a} \\to +\\infty\\)</span>, mais <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_1^{x_a} + \\dots + a_p^{x_a} \\to a_1^\\ell + \\dots + a_p^\\ell\\)</span>.</p>\n<p>Donc <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\ell = 0\\)</span>, et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_a\\ln a \\to \\ln p\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
